Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:04.11,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:07.55,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:11.04,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today is the legendary Snow Woman! A heart-chilling and sad case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:12.65,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.52,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:16.89,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
